sk.tomsik68.mclauncher.api.ui

Interface IProgressMonitor


  • public interface IProgressMonitor
    ProgressMonitors receive updates about different parts of MCLauncherAPI progress. It can be anything from a simple CLI up to dialog with a progress bar.

      • setProgress

        void setProgress(int progress)
        Sets current progress. Please note this value is between 0 and max_progress. You need to scale it yourself in order to get progress information between 0 and 100.
        Parameters:
        progress - New progress value
        See Also:
